	   <tr><td colspan=2>My guild killed Nortlav the Scalekeeper in "The Hole" and looted a red scale for one of our bards.  She already had the white scale I think.  Anyhow, what I heard from my fellow Nortlav killers was that he was RUMORED to drop the white scale VERY RARELY.  The point I am trying to make is that you should not consider Nortlav as a source of white scales.  <br><br>By the way, Nortlav is a total bastard to defeat in combat.  But, he is definitely killable with the right groups and levels.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
